"""
Optional local Django settings — machine-specific overrides.

Copy to local.py (same folder). local.py is gitignored and never overwritten by git pull.

Used by:
  - therese.settings        (development: loaded after base + dev)
  - therese.settings.base   (production: loaded at end of base.py)

Uncomment and adjust only what you need.
"""

